  "text": "MINISTRY OF WORKS & HOUSING NOTIFICATION New Delhi the 15th May, 1981 G.S.R. 351 (E).-In exercise of the powers conferred by sub-section (3) of section I of the Air (Prevention and Control Of Pollution) Act, 1981 (14 of 1981), the Central Government hereby appoints the 16th day of May, 1981,as the day on which the said Act shall come into force as the day on which thc said Act shall come into force. [Q-10012/4/78-EPC (Vol. IV)] S.R. ADIGE, Jt. Secy. Source: The Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 3 sub-section (i), New Delhi, Friday, May 15, 1981. -- 1 of 1 --",
